  (text "MCU: STM32G431CBT6. SPI1->DAC, I2C1->INA228, FDCAN1->TCAN1042 (VCC 5V bus\ndrive, VIO 3V3 logic). 8MHz crystal for CAN clock accuracy. OUT_REQ on PB14\n(PB4 NJTRST reset pull-up would close the disconnect at boot). Slot straps\nPB11-13 use internal pull-ups; backplane grounds them per slot." (at 15.24 33.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 5df7f3ac-8686-44da-b1f4-d6075ea3fa5b))
